Bruce Beasley Profile :
Dir., Pres., COO - Beasley Broadcast Group Inc. 

 


Bruce Beasley Biography :


Bruce G. Beasley has served as President, Chief Operating Officer of Beasley Broadcast Group since 1997. He began his career in the broadcasting industry with Beasley Broadcast Group in 1975 and has served in various capacities including General Sales Manager, General Manager of a major market radio station and as Vice President of Operations.Currently, Mr. Beasley oversees the operations of all Beasley Broadcast Group radio stations. He serves on the Board of Directors of the Radio Advertising Bureau. He graduated with a B.S. degree from East Carolina University. 

 


